name: How it all started! (part 2)
description:
2021, Gif, collage of an original painting and digital elements

Mary caught a fish, and asked Eli: “Do you still think that the BLUE sea is Boring? Well.. look. I'll show you!"

She took a knife and started stabbing the fish: “See the RED sea is much more fun!"

Elizabeth could no longer speak.  
Mary continued her massacre. The water turned red as blood. There was no more sound. The waves seemed dead.

Suddenly they heard Rania shouting: “Elizabeth, Elizabeth! Dinner is served! Good God, where are you?"
